\pard\f0\fs28 Like {\i Helictotrichon} but panicle spicate, with few spikelets; lower glume (3-)5-veined, the upper 5- to 7-veined; lemma deeply 2-dentate, with long, soft hairs below; awn arising from the sinus, geniculate, the basal part compressed and 3-veined; lodicules 3, hairy.
